open-udc README
===============

Copyright (c) 2010 The open-udc.org team. 

DESCRIPTION
-----------

Open-udc is an experimental implementation of an open monetary system.
It permit :
 - To create a currency and control its monetary mass.
 - To exchange money in this currency between individuals.
 - To apply Universal Dividend to the individuals that accept one universal digital currency.
And all of that with best efforts on security and anonymity preservation.

About Universal Dividend, please read the Theory of Money Relativity (in french: http://www.creationmonetaire.info/2010/11/theorie-relative-de-la-monnaie-10.html)


